+<li><a href="http://www.apache.org/">Apache 1.3.29</a> web server. The
+OpenBSD team has added <a href="faq10.html#httpdchroot">default
+chrooting</a>, privilege revocation, and other security-related
+improvements.  Also includes mod_ssl 2.8.16 and DSO support.
